# Links and hints

- **Internal links:** Use relative paths only (`api-reference/quickstart.md`). Never use `github.com`, `raw.githubusercontent.com`, or hardcoded `doc.keepnetlabs.com`. Do not use `[Endpoints](.)`.
- **New tab:** All links must open in new tab: `<a href="path" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Link text</a>`.
- **Direct links:** Use arrow-style inline links. Do not write "For more information, see X".
- **Hint blocks:** When using `{% hint style="info" %}`, include a platform doc link (e.g. **Company → Company Settings → REST API** and link to REST API Settings). Use `warning` for data loss, `danger` for deletion/security, `success` for best practices.

Reference: `DOCUMENTATION-RULES.md` (H3, H4, H5, H6, Internal links).
